      "name": "Non-cannulated Ti-6Al-4V pedicle screw, 7.5 mm diameter, ASTM F1717 static loading only",
      "description": "Assessment is applicable only to non-cannulated 7.5 mm diameter Ti-6Al-4V pedicle screw constructs tested under quasi-static ASTM F1717 compression-bending conditions. Results do not extend to cannulated designs, smaller diameter screws, dynamic fatigue loading, or materials other than Ti-6Al-4V."
    },
    "hasOperatingEnvelope": {
