      "rationale": "Material properties (E, Sy, Et) derived from coupon testing of Batch A Ti-6Al-4V material (n=6 tensile coupons per ASTM E8). Low confidence explicitly documented: n=6 yields wide 95% CI on Sy (+/-45 MPa) and n=4 for Et (+/-0.3 GPa). Uncertainty propagated via Monte Carlo (5000 samples). Sensitivity analysis confirms all QoIs remain within acceptance bounds at 95th percentile despite wide bounds. Geometry inputs from CMM measurement of production screws (n=5); dimensional uncertainty < 0.05 mm. Input uncertainty budget documented in report MI-2024-002.",
